 "headline": "Five-day pattern consistent with early cardiac decompensation: resting HR +9 bpm, nocturnal respiratory rate +3.2/min, activity down ~60%, weight +1.9 kg, and a downward SpO2 drift \u2014 all beginning 13 July. Temperature flat, arguing against infection. She has not reported feeling unwell.",
